snippet.title: ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN - Aces At War Ed. Trailer | PS4, X1
snippet.description:
The path is clear and the skies are ready for you! Introducing our Aces At War Bundle which includes the full game, a 150 page art book, and an exclusive Steelbook case. Order today and get it on Jan 18, 2019:

PS4 - https://bandainam.co/AcesatWarPS4
Xbox One - https://bandainam.co/AcesatWarX1
